title: Step2 2-in-1 Ford® F-150 SVT Raptor
description:
The 2-in-1 Ford® F-150 SVT Raptor by Step2 is the ultimate grow-with-me riding toy for your little truck lover! From a parent powered push buggy to a kid powered riding toy, the durable 2-in-1 Ford® F-150 SVT Raptor will be the coolest truck on the sidewalk. This ride-on truck has tons of realistic features to promote make believe fun and get little bodies active. 

Learn more at: http://www.step2.com/p/2-in-1-Ford-F-150-SVT-Raptor-Red
